description: Clear my cart on DoorDash app.
Open my latest saved news acticle on NewsBreak app and check comments.
In page 'Following', check latest posts and click the first one on the Quora app.
Upvote all contents I've bookmarked on the Quora app.
Check the log of latest answer I've bookmarked on Quora app.
Open Pinterest and open one of your own board.
Open Pinterest and search "DIY" in your own board list and open it.
Open the Trello app and add a new list titled "To Do" to the "School" board.
Open the Trello app, add a new card titled "Task 1" to the "To Do" list in the "School" board.
Open the Trello app and archive a list named "To Do" in the "School" board.
Open the Trello app and set a due date for a card in the "School" board.
On Zoom, start my scheduled meeting 'regular meeting' right now.
On Zoom, delete my scheduled meeting 'regular meeting'.
On Zoom, edit my scheduled meeting 'Weekly group meeting', set 'Repeat' to 'Every week'.
On Zoom, edit my scheduled meeting 'Weekly group meeting', turn 'Enable waiting room' on.
On Zoom, turn to page 'Team chat', bookmark my latest message to myself.
On Zoom, turn to page 'Team chat', set a reminder for my latest message to myself in 1 hour.
DoorDash, turn to the first one of saved stores, and add the most liked item to my cart.
DoorDash, turn to the first one of saved stores, start a group order and copy its link.
Turn to sever 'homework' and turn on 'Allow Direct Messages' on Discord app.
Go to Settings of server 'Agent Env' on Discord app.
Open Google Tasks and star "Task2".
Open Google Tasks and mark "Task2" as complete.
Open Google Tasks and delete the list "Test".
